        {
            "title": "滬指開市升8點 深成指升52點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市初段向上，上證綜指以4144點開市，升8點或0.21%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開市報14492點，亦升52點或0.37%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數升12點或0.27%，開報4715點；創業板指數開市報3365點，升16點或0.48%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15611503-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%e5%8d%878%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%88%90%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%8752%e9%bb%9e",
