        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段造好 恒指升94點報26844點 泡泡瑪特高開4.28%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股開市初段揚升，恒生指數開市報26844點，升94點或0.35%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數開報5801點，升3點或0.05%；國企指數以9188點開市，升27點或0.3%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：國泰君安國際官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240717_FI_source-web_01778.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：國泰君安國際官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240717_FI_source-web_01778.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：國泰君安國際官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國泰君安國際(01788)發盈喜，料去年盈利升最少2.65倍；該股今早開報2.77元，升2.59%。同樣發盈喜的尚有方舟健客(06086)，該公司估計去年扭虧為盈，股份今早開報3.12元，飆10.25%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">瑞和數智(03680)折讓約14%配股，該股今早開市不跌反升，以1.04元開市，漲14.29%；折讓18%配股的昇能集團(02459)同樣炒上，今早開報0.111元，升9.9%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"瑞和數智官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/03680-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"瑞和數智官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/03680-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">瑞和數智官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅股普遍造好，阿里巴巴(09988)開報169.5元，升0.59%；騰訊(00700)開報595元，暫時無升跌；美團(03690)開報97.94元，升0.41%；京東(09618)開報116元，升1.05%；小米(01810)開報36.36元，升0.33%。泡泡瑪特(09992)今早再漲4.28%，以229元開市。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250714_FI_source-web_09992-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250714_FI_source-web_09992-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：泡泡瑪特官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">至於兩大藍籌國際金融股，滙控(00005)開報130元，暫時無升跌；友邦(01299)開報84.1元，升1.26%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15611498-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e9%80%a0%e5%a5%bd-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%8794%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126844%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b3%a1%e6%b3%a1%e7%91%aa%e7%89%b9%e9%ab%98%e9%96%8b4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-26 09:34:28",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美佳音配股  折讓18.7%提全購今復牌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美佳音(06939)公布，向獨立第三方Geehy出售股份並配售新股，依例提全面收購，作價0.61元，較上日收市價折讓18.7%，股份今復牌。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公司公布，向Geehy出售2.11億股股份，相當已發行股本總額約40.67%，即每股銷售股份0.50元，總代價為1.055億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">此外，公司將向Geehy發行1.0375億股新，認購價每股0.61元，佔經擴大已發行股本約16.67%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">交易完成後公司所得款項淨額6128.75萬元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">全部交易完成後Geehy佔經擴大已發行股本約50.56%。因此根據收購守則規則26.1須提全面收購，作價每股0.61元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公司上午九時恢復買賣。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15611465-%e7%be%8e%e4%bd%b3%e9%9f%b3%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1-%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%9318-7%e6%8f%90%e5%85%a8%e8%b3%bc%e4%bb%8a%e5%be%a9%e7%89%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-26 09:22:38",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "即月期指開報26797點 高水47點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指開報26797點，升79點，較上日現貨收市價26749點高水47點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月科指期貨開報5797點，升10點，低水1點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月國指期貨開報9177點，升26點，高水16點。</p>\n</div>",
